rows.label: tlk44300183_01_msg0001
rows.name:
My, my. You've come from the
outside, haven't you? Well then,
you must find our city quite cold?

rows.label: tlk44300183_01_msg0002
rows.name:
Here, we use the power of
Ether for warmth... But
yes, it is cold. Rather.

rows.label: tlk44300183_01_msg0003
rows.name:
To fight the cold we eat Stralu and
Adel's Embercakes. And drink... Oh,
minors are present? Never mind, then.
